title: Faq - Hidden PayPal
html:
Hidden PayPal

About Us Products FAQ Contacts

FAQ

Frequently asked questions

Why don't you cash out these accounts by yourself?

â Of course, we do. But it's very suspicious to cash out 100-200 accounts per month. So, It's better business for us to sell these to individual people, who can really cash it out.

How can I trust you?

â We're not new people in TOR, so we know how many scammers appeared here, and we want to change it. You can check reviews of our service on different catalogues or forums. Also we can provide you a video recording proving the account is valid and has the exact balance shown in our table.

How do you get these accounts?

â We gain access to PayPal accounts by using various methods, such as phishing, malware, and social engineering. Phishing involves sending emails that appear to be from PayPal, but are actually from a malicious actor. These emails often contain malicious links or attachments that can be used to gain access to a userâs account. Malware is another method used by us to gain access to PayPal accounts. Malware is spiteful software that can be installed on a userâs computer and used to steal login credentials or other sensitive information. Social engineering is also used by our specialists to get data about PayPal accounts. This involves using deception or manipulation to trick users into revealing their login credentials or other sensitive information.

How it works?

â We offer you the details from PayPal.com accounts. After pushing 'Buy' button you have to contact us via Email and make a payment. Then our manager will send you all related data to Log In. Once logged in, you have full access to all the options and all owner information, such as data of linked bank cards.

If something goes wrong, can I get my money back?

â Yes. We realize that any system can fail and errors can happen everywhere. That's why we have 24/7 support via Email. We are sure to solve any problem you have, all you have to do is describe it in detail.

How can I pay?

â Only with cryptocurrency. We accept BTC, ETH, LTC, USDT and almost all other.
